    "translatedContent": "**Q**: I'm still uncertain, is there more ?<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 63,
    "rowsha": "550k0kxi6mytVwWRv+9BhpAK+My2B2rJmJI64F8TV90=",
    "originContent": "**A**: Yes, Have a look at the [documentation](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Smurf-IV/Elucidate/master/./docs/Documentation.md) for pictures etc.",
    "translatedContent": "**A**: Yes, have a look at the [documentation](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Smurf-IV/Elucidate/master/./docs/Documentation.md) for pictures etc."
